---spike_Rampage Explosive---
Auras :: [[Rampage Explosive]]

---aura_Rampage Explosive---
Type :: Buff
Duration :: -1
Icon :: 
Max Stacks :: 1
Time Per Tick :: 1.0
Definitions :: [[Custom:RampageExplosive]]

---ability_Rampage Explosion---
Bullet Definition :: [[rampageexplosion]]
Max Range :: 100.0
